TEXT(&beginproblem);

$y = random(8.5,8.7,.001);
$e = random(91,99,.05);

$pre = $y/($e*100);
$ans1= round($pre*1000000)/1000000;
&ANS(num_cmp($ans1));



TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The premium of a 100-strike yen-denominated put on the euro is $y Yen.  The current exchange rate is $e Yen/euro. 

 $BR

What is its premium\{ans_rule(20)\}euro?

EOT



